Thence N 02° 57' 20" E, along the westerly line of the remainder piece of said Original 7.3695 acre tract, along the easterly line of said Rule of 3, LLC tract, along the easterly line of a tract of land conveyed to Stanislaus S. Liu, Tr. of record in Instrument Number 201301160008641 and along the easterly line of a tract of land conveyed to Jordan Rentals II, LLC of record in Instrument Number 201112290170141, 540.0± feet to a northeasterly comer of said Jordan Rentals II, LLC tract and the southeasterly comer of said Central Ohio Community Improvement Corporation tract;
